## Usage Grant

The Licensor grants you the right to copy, modify, create derivative works, 
redistribute, and make non-production use of the Licensed Work. The Licensor 
grants you a limited production-use license if your use does not exceed 
100 stored secrets per instance.

Production use exceeding 100 secrets requires a commercial license from the Licensor.

## Additional Use Grant

You may make production use of the Licensed Work if:
- Your use does not exceed 100 secrets per instance, OR
- You have purchased a commercial license

## Notice

On the Change Date, the license automatically converts to Apache License 2.0.

